{"tid":745254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國警察再輸出海外　首度克羅地亞執勤　協助內地旅客","createTime":"2018-07-16T14:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T00:58:48.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dbfb5abe56290932e5d6383478531fea667f7f3f","tid":745254,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>中國警察再輸出海外　首度克羅地亞執勤　協助中國旅客</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/croatia-10_9HOgG_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcroatia-10_9HOgG_1200x0.png&h=071bada7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n克羅地亞昨天打入世界盃決賽，創下國家歷史。不過該國昨天還有另一項歷史誕生，就是容許中國警察在該國執勤的《中克兩國旅遊季警務聯巡項目》昨天啟動，令克羅地亞繼意大利後，第二個與中國警方開展警備聯合巡邏的國家。<br />\n<br />\n根據外交部駐港特派員公署facebook專頁公佈，中國駐克羅地亞大使胡兆明、公安部相關負責人、克旅遊部國務秘書、警察總局副局長等出席啟動儀式。<br />\n<br />\n胡兆明指，聯巡是兩國加強政治互信和執法合作的體現，而克羅地亞打入世界盃決賽將大大增加中國遊客人數，聯巡將為向中國民眾推介克羅地亞，發揮積極作用。當然，事情最後總會和「一帶一路」有關，胡兆明指，中方希望與克羅地亞共享發展成果，也希望共同促進「一帶一路」沿線安全。<br />\n<br />\n從圖片可見，中國男女警察約6人，在克警的陪同下，於薩格勒布街頭巡邏。這6名警員來自公安部國際合作局，以及廣東省公安廳。<br />\n<br />\n除了首都薩格勒布外，阿德里亞海城市杜布羅夫尼克，以及普利特維采湖群國家公園(Plitvice Lakes National Park)都會見到中國警察身影，他們會執勤約一個月。外交部專頁引述中國遊客表示，「能在距離祖國萬里之外的克羅地亞看到中國警察的身影，感到特別興奮、特別安全。」中國遊客遍佈全球，究竟中國警察要走到多遠呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%86%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%86%8D%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96-%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E5%85%8B%E7%BE%85%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%9E%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4-%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%258E%25B2%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%2586%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%259F%25B7%25E5%258B%25A4-%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%2F&d=592NbAX12gRHz7hn00hMX%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e6fe45a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%258E%25B2%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%2586%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%259F%25B7%25E5%258B%25A4-%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%2F&h=560bc44d\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%86%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%86%8D%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96-%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E5%85%8B%E7%BE%85%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%9E%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4-%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2/</a><br />\n<br />\n一個個慢慢滲透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53966e7f1463715e41b9d9075cce4678b6ce922","tid":745254,"uid":3646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3a8e518e59f370a8c02a247f1ab62573391a93","tid":745254,"uid":52946,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"facebook專頁公佈 大陸都上唔到比邊個睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e60f082593b7b7206593b59e333717da4f749e","tid":